EN: This report, therefore, received high praise.

ZH: 他的行为不够谨慎，因而造成了很大的麻烦。
EN: His careless behavior, therefore, caused a lot of trouble.

ZH: 他一直认真学习，因而成绩非常优秀。
EN: He has been studying diligently, and thus his grades are excellent.

ZH: 他经常运动，因而保持身体健康。
EN: He exercises regularly, hence he maintains good health.

ZH: 我不喜欢团队合作，因而我更喜欢独自完成任务。
EN: I don't like teamwork, hence I prefer to complete tasks alone.

ZH: 他很了解市场需求，因而他的产品畅销。
EN: He understands the market demand well, resulting in the high sales of his products.

ZH: 这个国家的稳定政策因而吸引了很多外国投资者。
EN: The stable policies of this country thus attract many foreign investors.

ZH: 他不懂得沟通，因而他的问题没有得到解决。
EN: He lacks communication skills, therefore his problems remain unresolved.

ZH: 这个球队打得太不合作了，因而输掉了比赛。
EN: This team played in a disorganized manner, and hence lost the game.

ZH: 因而的天气预报表明明天会下雨。
EN: Therefore, the weather forecast indicates that it will rain tomorrow.

