EN: This news thus attracted the attention of many people.

ZH: 因而的研究结果证明这种方法十分有效。
EN: Therefore, the research results prove that this method is very effective.

ZH: 他缺乏经验，因而不被公司录取。
EN: He lacks experience, hence he was not hired by the company.

